1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,290
Tom's goal does not pilot him in vague generalities.

2
00:00:04,400 --> 00:00:07,970
It gives him specific directions in all his activities.

3
00:00:08,079 --> 00:00:13,170
When Tom buys a suit, the goal speaks and shows Tom the wise choice.

4
00:00:13,599 --> 00:00:18,369
The goal helps to show Tom what steps to take to move up to the next job,

5
00:00:18,480 --> 00:00:23,089
what to say in the business conference, what to do when conflict develops,

6
00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:25,730
what to read, what stand to take.

7
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:33,889
Should Tom drift a little off course, his automatic instrumentation, housed securely in his subconscious mind,

8
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:38,129
alerts him and tells him what to do to get back on course.

9
00:00:39,520 --> 00:00:45,409
Tom's goal has made him super sensitive to all the many forces at work that affect him.

10
00:00:46,240 --> 00:00:52,930
Jack, on the other hand, lacking a goal, also lacks the automatic instrumentation to guide him.

11
00:00:53,120 --> 00:00:55,089
He is easily confused.

12
00:00:55,280 --> 00:00:58,450
His actions reflect no personal policy.

13
00:00:58,720 --> 00:01:02,609
Jack wavers, shifts, guesses at what to do.

14
00:01:02,880 --> 00:01:08,849
Lacking consistency of purpose, Jack flounders on the ruddy road to mediocrity.

15
00:01:10,160 --> 00:01:14,210
May I suggest you listen to this section again right now.

16
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:16,530
Let this concept soak in.

17
00:01:16,640 --> 00:01:18,290
Then, look around you.

18
00:01:18,480 --> 00:01:22,050
Study the very top echelon of successful persons.

19
00:01:22,240 --> 00:01:27,250
Note how they, without exception, are totally devoted to their objective.

20
00:01:27,520 --> 00:01:33,490
Observe how the life of a highly successful person is integrated around a purpose.

21
00:01:34,079 --> 00:01:35,889
Surrender to that goal.

22
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:37,329
Really surrender.

23
00:01:37,440 --> 00:01:44,290
Let it obsess you and give you the automatic instrumentation you need to reach that goal.

24
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:51,409
On occasion, all of us have waked up on Saturday morning with no plans,

25
00:01:51,520 --> 00:01:56,369
no agenda, either mental or written, that spells out what we're going to do.

26
00:01:56,800 --> 00:01:59,810
On days like that, we accomplish next to nothing.
